 executive officer of lyondellbasell in houston texas in  succeeding volker trautz as part of a reorganization following us bankruptcy court proceedings gallogly guided the company out of chapter  bankruptcy and successfully repositioned it as one of the worlds largest refining companies and makers of polymers and petrochemicals gallogly formally retired as ceo of lyondellbasell in january  as of february   he was appointed as a director of dupont awardsedit petrochemical heritage award  icis kavaler award  honorary doctorate of science university of colorado colorado springs  communication leadership award  from the houston chapter of the international association of business communicators philanthropyedit on behalf of the gallogly family foundation james and janet gallogly pledged to donate m to the university of colorado supporting creation of the gallogly events center the center is named in honor of father tommy m gallogly a nontraditional adult student who earned bachelors  and masters degrees  in education at uccs formally dedicated in  the building has been awarded leadership in energy and environmental design leed gold certification referencesedit  a b c d gallogly jim march   from smokestacks to emerald cities texas technology showcase   a b c jim gallogly ceo dossier world of ceos retrieved  july    a b lyondellbasell names jim gallogly as ceo may   retrieved  july    a b lyondellbasell announces retirement of ceo jim gallogly  houston and london sept   prnewswire  prnewswirecom retrieved may     a b dupont appoints edward d breen and james l gallogly to board of directors  dupont usa dupontcom february   retrieved may     a b family to dedicate uccs gallogly events center university of colorado foundation retrieved  july    phillips board oks changes in management the journal record december   retrieved  july    phillips board oks management changes the journal record august   retrieved  july    christopher j castaneda phillips petroleum company encyclop